extends layout

block content
	div.container
		h4 What is Wordentropy?
		p
			| We all know 
			a[href="http://xkcd.com/936/"] passwords suck.
		p
			| Passphrases are better, but you still have to create some kind of mnemonic to make a random group of words easy to remember.
		p
			| Wordentropy tries to do this for you by creating a pseudo-grammatical "sentence" of random English words. This allows you to create a strong passphrase that's also easy to remember.
